{"tid":1551142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇搞錯？咁大個核彈出面都唔推？一點半遮打花園呀！","createTime":"2019-09-08T00:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T02:17:20.000Z","uid":232014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b81fbcfe45300663095d84cfd94888c558338c8","tid":1551142,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:33:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登係咪比五毛入侵哂定大家覺得已經贏左？<br />\n<br />\n出面熱門可以一個post都冇？呢個人權法案等左我地幾耐呀？口口聲聲話要推呢個法案簽哂啲聯署，到行動果日可以一個post都冇？有冇搞錯呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有咩問題自己睇啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[美領] 請入黎聽我講點解今日9月8號集會遊行要準時，並且完結後和平散去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550879</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［有圖］驚嫂表示老公常OT，每天要自慰3次解決<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日 <br />\n下晝一點半<br />\n遮打花園<br />\n行到美國領事館<br />\n<br />\n一定要推到人權法案制裁班仆街！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1tnduK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1tnduK.png&h=4bcfd183&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TzBhWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TzBhWq.png&h=5f0851b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81d40a0b4ffe9570d3cc6e1b975c51724231ac3c","tid":1551142,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門<br />\n未上到熱門唔會停"},{"pid":"704e9d049c7228cb49c915613d04694d2105ec61","tid":1551142,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2525139ed7c4638eaa189fd7639cbba9ef677c5","tid":1551142,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T